#: lib/retro_hex_chat_web/controllers/help_content/feature_flood_protection.html.heex:2
#, elixir-autogen, elixir-format
msgid ""
"Flood Protection automatically detects and handles various types of abuse, "
"including message flooding and duplicate spam. All detection runs on your "
"side — other users are not affected."
